h: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Bitcatcha helped us determine these web hosting providersâ€™ server response times across geographical locations, including the US, London, Singapore, SÃ£o Paulo, India, Sydney, and Japan.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Beyond the Best Hosting for WordPress</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this guide to the best WordPress hosting companies helped you find the right option for your hosting needs. Now that you know how to choose the top WordPress host, you should learn <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\">about WordPress website optimization</a> to drive more traffic and improve SEO rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To dig even further into running a WordPress site, check out these articles and tutorials:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-hacks-to-grow-your-traffic/\">30 SEO Hacks Guaranteed to Grow Your Traffic</a></li><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-cache-plugin/\">Best WordPress Cache Plugins</a></li><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-move-a-wordpress-site-to-a-new-domain/\">How to Move a WordPress Site to a New Domain</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Thatâ€™s all for today! Donâ€™t forget to follow us on social media and bookmark our site for more tips on search engine optimization, WordPress hosting services, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-hosting/\">7+ Best WordPress Hosting Services for 2022 (Compared & Tested)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-hosting/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s